# Summary
This documentation page describes the Aampe Cohort Sync integration, which allows real-time syncing of Amplitude cohorts to Aampe for personalized messaging across multiple channels (SMS, email, push, in-app), requiring an Aampe API key and proper user ID mapping configuration.

